# Cursor Rules for URL Shortener Project

## Code Style
- Use ESLint for code formatting and linting
- Auto-fix on save should work with ESLint
- Remove excessive blank lines (max 1 blank line)
- Use 2 spaces for indentation
- Use single quotes for strings
- Add semicolons at end of statements

## File Structure
- Keep TypeScript files in src/
- Use .js extensions for imports in ESM mode
- Follow Express.js best practices

## Linting
- Run `pnpm lint` to check for issues
- Run `pnpm lint:fix` to auto-fix issues
- ESLint should handle blank line removal automatically
